---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Offerings"
  description="Private therapeutic and sacred bodywork sessions, offered one-on-one. Each session is a meeting point between structural work for the body and something deeper."
  canonicalPath="/offerings"
>
  {/* Page Hero */}
  <section class="bg-bg-dark pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-gold mb-6">Offerings</h1>
      <p class="text-text-inverse/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Sessions are offered privately, one-on-one. Each is a meeting point between therapeutic and sacred &mdash; structural work for the body, held in a container that honors something deeper.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Therapeutic Sessions */}
  <section class="bg-bg-light py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-accent/10 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center">
          <p class="text-muted text-sm italic text-center px-6">
            Image: therapeutic session
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="w-10 h-[2px] bg-gold mb-6"></div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">
            Therapeutic Sessions
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            [Therapeutic session description — approx. 80 words. This describes the structural, body-focused work: what modalities are used, what the experience feels like, what outcomes clients can expect. Provided by client.]
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-muted mt-6">
            <p><span class="font-medium text-text">Duration:</span> [e.g., 60–90 minutes]</p>
            <p><span class="font-medium text-text">What to expect:</span> [Brief note on what a session involves]</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Sacred Sessions */}
  <section class="bg-bg-light py-24 md:py-32 border-t border-accent/10">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <div class="w-10 h-[2px] bg-gold mb-6"></div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">
            Sacred Sessions
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            [Sacred session description — approx. 80 words. This describes the more energetic or ceremonial dimension of the work: its roots, the intention behind it, what distinguishes it from the therapeutic offering. Provided by client.]
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-muted mt-6">
            <p><span class="font-medium text-text">Duration:</span> [e.g., 90–120 minutes]</p>
            <p><span class="font-medium text-text">What to expect:</span> [Brief note on what a session involves]</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 aspect-[4/3] bg-accent/10 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center">
          <p class="text-muted text-sm italic text-center px-6">
            Image: sacred session
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Pricing & Location */}
  <section class="bg-bg-light py-24 md:py-32 border-t border-accent/10">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-accent mb-6">
        Pricing &amp; Location
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        Sessions are offered in [cities/regions]. Pricing varies by location and context. To inquire or book, reach out directly.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
        <a href="/contact#booking" class="btn-secondary">Book a discovery call</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
